snippet.title: Do You Like Spaghetti Ice Cream? Super Simple Song by Kids Diana Show
snippet.description:
"Do You Like Spaghetti Ice Cream?" is an original and very simple food song by Kids Diana Show. Created for teaching how to express food likes and dislikes, and asking and answering "Do you like _______?" questions. Super Simple Song by Kids Diana Show
